ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e8cf6f3ceb82c9e5b55f0a25c6e169e47f8572","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人去唔怕悶咩？ <br />\n危險？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n悶就一時時啦，行得耐會好想講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但其實一個人好free<br />\n危險就都唔驚得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去左先算"},{"pid":"af43f72e48687bd2ca19eb609ebc7f25c7f871c5","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩樓主受屌識改<br />\n一開波見到d女孩女孩同d夾硬來既書面語真係屌晒鬼<br />\n<br />\nbtw繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身想呈現個效果出唔到黎，可能西藏篇開個新po算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644d9c65a24908d62386b350d5a3433006b96eb2","tid":49418,"uid":58101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d886b13bf5573e54fab7bdf24e37dc27d967e7c3","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"之前在麗江找古城入口時，遇到個泰國佬<br />\n原來他也要去古城，於是兩個人on99的等巴士，問路<br />\n然後發覺兜了一個大圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得好像fake了泰國佬，有點不好意思，於是向他介紹我住的客棧<br />\n後來行古城又遇到泰國佬，原來他是個大學教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不知為何看起來那麼頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後兩人又分別了，繼續各自走自己的路<br />\n<br />\n轉眼已到旅程的第七日<br />\n今日要去香格里拉<br />\n大陸很多客運站都設有麵店，隨便吃了個午餐<br />\n之後就搭大巴上路<br />\n在大陸坐大巴坐三、四個鐘是等閒事，本身以為會見到地獄鬼國最無文化的一面，可幸全部都好正常<br />\n無人隨地大小便，無偷竊<br />\n另外市區內的巴士，有好多少數民族婦女，感覺幾慈祥<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉古城在數年前的一場大火，破壞了大部分建築<br />\n古城內很多地方都在重建，感覺好冷清<br />\n<br />\n在平均海拔三千米的土地，呼吸開始有點急速，心跳也有點加快<br />\n隨便找了家藏民餐廳解決晚餐<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8N2oZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8N2oZQ.jpg&h=f10db7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藏餐大部分是牦牛肉，酥油茶，藏麵<br />\n個人不太喜歡，但個店員好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n古城內有間賣明信片的店，可以坐下慢慢寫明信片，幾有feel<br />\n其實每次旅行都喜歡找時間坐下慢慢寫明信片<br />\n因為你可以趁機回憶旅程的種種<br />\n突然聽到一句好熟悉的話：屌你老母！<br />\n原來在異地聽到廣東話粗口係咁感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n看來是香港人，大家對望了一秒，彼此心照不宣地笑了"},{"pid":"139c59a753503f7e1ac009e033a123606116bac7","tid":49418,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意小明風格喔，好正<br />\n<br />\nBtw 絲打好似每個地方都蜻蜓點水式遊玩<br />\n而且仲要跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又冇包車遊洱海/瀘沽湖<br />\nMiss 左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b50fef2530bc17513b38e143e04925a03a9d723","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好鍾意小明風格喔，好正<br />\n<br />\nBtw 絲打好似每個地方都蜻蜓點水式遊玩<br />\n而且仲要跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又冇包車遊洱海/瀘沽湖<br />\nMiss 左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭想試下用內心獨立表達對果個地方既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過寫得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我日日都係去到果到先plan行程，晒左好多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8454767ceea9f0b2bf3d933de0a83e51dbb877","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好鍾意小明風格喔，好正<br />\n<br />\nBtw 絲打好似每個地方都蜻蜓點水式遊玩<br />\n而且仲要跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又冇包車遊洱海/瀘沽湖<br />\nMiss 左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭想試下用內心獨<span style=\"color: red;\">白</span>表達對果個地方既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過寫得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我日日都係去到果到先plan行程，晒左好多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82ee7ca722089a0e49e817fb596bb6e087b49d8","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:04:27.000Z","msg":"大陸人好鐘意給小孩著開襠褲<br />\n客棧老闆娘的小孩當然不例外，小孩純真的臉，和他的開襠褲，形成一種好神奇的化學作用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8kV10H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8kV10H.jpg&h=047933e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開襠褲概念圖<br />\n<br />\n在香格里拉睡了一個晚上，開始適應高海拔<br />\n早上出發去普達措森林公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6FK9dV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6FK9dV.jpg&h=cfe7e7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/164620_28ac97536e9cc097d2e3879e0d478667.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F164620_28ac97536e9cc097d2e3879e0d478667.jpg&h=bc71a629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公園好大，點與點之間要坐接駁巴士<br />\n巴士開得好快，旁邊是山，快到好像要發出山一般，<br />\n大陸人好不怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6月尾應該不是去普達措的最佳季節，沒有想像中的花海<br />\n所以走馬看花走完一圈，就去納帕海<br />\n納帕海其實是個草原，可以騎馬<br />\n其實我不想騎馬，我覺得隻馬好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但經不起草原負責人推銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n騎到一半，去到一個叫情人谷的地方，那是一個無人之境<br />\n放眼整片草原一個遊客也沒有，只有幾個農民<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/165932_b40bac9fd80848a87e91ed7b6c9908db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F165932_b40bac9fd80848a87e91ed7b6c9908db.jpg&h=5e856691&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GM53mQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGM53mQX.jpg&h=719a46b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yg3Bi88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyg3Bi88.jpg&h=61a765b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來我跟天空如此接近，我好想大叫<br />\n會當凌絕頂 一覽眾山小！！！！！<br />\n開始覺得草原大媽沒有騙我，好值得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/170332_e2d437352281ba2d2ee77b9c23436683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F170332_e2d437352281ba2d2ee77b9c23436683.jpg&h=0d64b432&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/170333_3763a474161554a362015a1bb961c32a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F170333_3763a474161554a362015a1bb961c32a.jpg&h=6ccf2c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n納帕海入面一些小村莊"},{"pid":"9288eaf437acff14e7cf342d1f6edcc5acaf994a","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"夜晚去藏民晚宴，$150一人<br />\n都是歌舞表演，飯菜一般啦<br />\n我發覺因為每餐都是隨便吃的關係，對雲南美食的記憶好模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m5X8t5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm5X8t5J.jpg&h=ff48ed67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/172515_8a78f6f2b406746b0493374ea9ddc55b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F172515_8a78f6f2b406746b0493374ea9ddc55b.jpg&h=1a686792&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/172518_69c625ffd960b67dae1006c01c205ab3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F172518_69c625ffd960b67dae1006c01c205ab3.jpg&h=a769a8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不建議去藏民晚宴，有點搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明天回麗江，坐夜晚的火車回昆明，後天再去成都坐青藏鐵路了"},{"pid":"865e63040e2fcfce1b9815fc2e053740293e9f52","tid":49418,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"其實雲南之旅已到尾聲，一向見步行步的性格<br />\n令我錯過了不少風景<br />\n當然天氣也是決定性的一環<br />\n可惜時間不容我停留細看<br />\n<br />\n在香格里拉的最後一夜，喝了幾杯青稞酒<br />\n一邊聽歌舞表演，一邊聽旁邊的大媽鳩up<br />\n人生的意義仍未找到，但學會了享受獨處<br />\n<br />\n之後兩日都是搭大巴，火車，飛機，略過不提<br />\n旅程第十日，準備踏上青藏鐵路，44小時不洗澡的日子<br />\n<br />\n睇黎書面語寫得麻麻，西藏部分應該會開新post，有興趣可以睇下，無興趣都係果句，唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adebf33c245c6f2bb5f85027f3da1512053863d2","tid":49418,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"一定支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去大陸唔好去咩民族探訪是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}